프로젝트 `D:\16. 자동화 도구\safeAutoTest`에서 작업합니다. `lib/site-types.ts`와 `jsdom`이 이미 설치돼 있습니다.

**목표:** `lib/dom-normalizer.ts`와 `tests/unit/dom-normalizer.test.ts`를 TDD로 생성하고 커밋합니다.

**규칙:** 이 두 파일만 건드리세요. 다른 파일 절대 수정 금지.

---

**Step 1: `tests/unit/dom-normalizer.test.ts` 생성**

```ts
import test from "node:test";
import assert from "node:assert/strict";
import { normalizeHtmlString } from "../../lib/dom-normalizer.ts";
import type { DomConfig } from "../../lib/site-types.ts";

const baseConfig: DomConfig = {
  enabled: true,
  ignoreSelectors: [],
  normalizeWhitespace: true,
};

test("removes script/style/noscript", () => {
  const { serialized } = normalizeHtmlString(
    `<html><body><script>x</script><style>y</style><noscript>z</noscript><p>keep</p></body></html>`,
    baseConfig
  );
  assert.ok(serialized.includes("keep"));
  assert.ok(!serialized.includes("script"));
  assert.ok(!serialized.includes("style"));
  assert.ok(!serialized.includes("noscript"));
});

test("removes ignoreSelectors matches", () => {
  const { serialized } = normalizeHtmlString(
    `<html><body><p>keep</p><div class="ad">drop</div></body></html>`,
    { ...baseConfig, ignoreSelectors: [".ad"] }
  );
  assert.ok(serialized.includes("keep"));
  assert.ok(!serialized.includes("drop"));
});

test("normalizes whitespace in text nodes", () => {
  const { serialized } = normalizeHtmlString(
    `<html><body><p>a   b\n\nc</p></body></html>`,
    baseConfig
  );
  assert.ok(serialized.includes("a b c"));
});

test("sorts attributes alphabetically", () => {
  const { serialized } = normalizeHtmlString(
    `<html><body><a href="x" class="c" id="i">t</a></body></html>`,
    baseConfig
  );
  const idx = (s: string) => serialized.indexOf(s);
  assert.ok(idx("class=") < idx("href="));
  assert.ok(idx("href=") < idx("id="));
});

test("same input -> same hash", () => {
  const html = `<html><body><p>hi</p></body></html>`;
  const a = normalizeHtmlString(html, baseConfig);
  const b = normalizeHtmlString(html, baseConfig);
  assert.equal(a.hash, b.hash);
  assert.equal(a.hash.length, 64);
});

test("different input -> different hash", () => {
  const a = normalizeHtmlString(`<html><body><p>a</p></body></html>`, baseConfig);
  const b = normalizeHtmlString(`<html><body><p>b</p></body></html>`, baseConfig);
  assert.notEqual(a.hash, b.hash);
});

test("masks auto-generated id-like attribute values", () => {
  const { hash: h1 } = normalizeHtmlString(
    `<html><body><div aria-describedby="tooltip-a1b2c3">t</div></body></html>`,
    baseConfig
  );
  const { hash: h2 } = normalizeHtmlString(
    `<html><body><div aria-describedby="tooltip-x9y8z7">t</div></body></html>`,
    baseConfig
  );
  assert.equal(h1, h2);
});
```

**Step 2: 테스트 실패 확인**
```bash
cd "D:\16. 자동화 도구\safeAutoTest" && npx tsx --test tests/unit/dom-normalizer.test.ts 2>&1 | head -5
```
"Cannot find module" 오류가 나야 정상.

**Step 3: `lib/dom-normalizer.ts` 생성**

```ts
import { createHash } from "node:crypto";
import { JSDOM } from "jsdom";
import type { DomConfig } from "./site-types.ts";

const ID_LIKE_ATTR_PATTERN = /-?[a-z0-9]{6,}/gi;
const ID_BEARING_ATTRS = new Set([
  "aria-describedby",
  "aria-labelledby",
  "aria-controls",
  "aria-owns",
  "id",
  "for",
]);

export interface NormalizeResult {
  serialized: string;
  hash: string;
}

export function normalizeHtmlString(html: string, config: DomConfig): NormalizeResult {
  const dom = new JSDOM(html);
  const document = dom.window.document;

  document.querySelectorAll("script, style, noscript").forEach((n) => n.remove());
  for (const selector of config.ignoreSelectors) {
    document.querySelectorAll(selector).forEach((n) => n.remove());
  }

  walk(document.body, config);

  const serialized = document.body ? document.body.outerHTML : "";
  const hash = createHash("sha256").update(serialized).digest("hex");

  return { serialized, hash };
}

function walk(node: Element | null, config: DomConfig): void {
  if (!node) return;

  if (node.attributes) {
    const attrs = Array.from(node.attributes);
    const sorted = attrs
      .map((a) => ({
        name: a.name,
        value: ID_BEARING_ATTRS.has(a.name)
          ? a.value.replace(ID_LIKE_ATTR_PATTERN, "<id>")
          : a.value,
      }))
      .sort((x, y) => x.name.localeCompare(y.name));

    for (const a of attrs) node.removeAttribute(a.name);
    for (const { name, value } of sorted) node.setAttribute(name, value);
  }

  for (const child of Array.from(node.childNodes)) {
    if (child.nodeType === 3) {
      if (config.normalizeWhitespace && child.textContent) {
        child.textContent = child.textContent.replace(/\s+/g, " ").trim();
      }
    } else if (child.nodeType === 1) {
      walk(child as Element, config);
    }
  }
}
```

**Step 4: 테스트 통과 확인**
```bash
cd "D:\16. 자동화 도구\safeAutoTest" && npx tsx --test tests/unit/dom-normalizer.test.ts 2>&1
```
7/7 PASS여야 합니다.

**Step 5: 커밋**
```bash
cd "D:\16. 자동화 도구\safeAutoTest" && git add lib/dom-normalizer.ts tests/unit/dom-normalizer.test.ts && git commit -m "feat(site): add dom-normalizer with jsdom-based tests"
```

결과를 한 줄로 보고하세요: "PASS 7/7, committed" 또는 실패 내용.

